pinolo, the naughty irc bot
===========================

Requirements
------------
See included ``requirements.txt`` file, which can be passed to ``pip`` for an
easy installation of the required packages.

- python >= 2.5
- Twisted
- Yapsy
- PyPubSub
- SQLAlchemy (optional)
- xapian (optional, can only be installed with ``easy_install``?)

Notes
-----
The code is messy and ugly.

